Build a GUIDE-based replacement for xrolo.
Use structured fields, initially hard-coded:
Company|Contact|Street|City|Province|Code|W|X|V|D|H|M
store in (two) flat files, one in home and one public.
Let insert into either, if found show which one.
Have both detail display and one-line (co, person, w, x, v, h, m) or full,
selectable by view menu.
